# outputs

**Instance Property**

An array of audio output port descriptions.

## Declaration

```swift
var outputs: [AVAudioSessionPortDescription] { get }
```

## Discussion

This property contains an array of [doc://com.apple.avfaudio/documentation/AVFAudio/AVAudioSessionPortDescription] objects representing the audio outputs associated with the current audio route for a session.

## Getting the Input and Output Ports

- **inputs**: An array of audio input port descriptions.
